{
  "stem": "4078.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I would hear church bells all the time, and I would wake up absolutely petrified that they were coming in to get us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "13. 12, 13, Yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, I was getting smarter, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was-- then I went to another school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I won a scholarship.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I sat for it and I passed it to go to this Chiswick Polytechnic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was very happy about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there until 194-- 1944, because the-- the rockets started coming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I became petrified of these rockets, and they were dreadful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At least with a plane, you heard the plane, and you heard it come over, and then you heard it disappear.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With the rockets, it was entirely different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The V-1s, you heard this plane, and you knew it because it had a-- a very distinct sound, a chug, chug, chug.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the-- the thing was, the engine would shut off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You'd hear this chug, chug, chug, chug, chug, and the engine would shut off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you immediately, as soon as the engine shut off, you immediately made a dive for under the bed or under a table or somewhere safe.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then you heard an explosion, and that was how the V-1s were released.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- they themselves were the bombs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the V-2s were a bigger-scale thing, and they just devastated whole streets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I got very, very petrified and very nervous, and my mother took me away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My father couldn't leave, but my mother took me away to the north of England, to a place called Newcastle, where the coals come from, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to stay with her sister.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And her sister was more Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, she practiced Judaism.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
